sparql: PREFIX yago: <http://dbpedia.org/class/yago/> PREFIX dbp: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?uri rdf:type yago:WikicatStatesOfTheUnitedStates ; dbp:densityrank ?rank } ORDER BY ASC(?rank) LIMIT 1

sparql2nl.en: What is the least densely populated state in the United States?
sparql2nl.original_en: Which state of the USA has the highest population density?
sparql2nl.prompt:
Assume you have to rephrase the following SPARQL query as a natural-language question for non-technical humans. 
Use the English language. SPARQL query: 
PREFIX yago: <http://dbpedia.org/class/yago/> PREFIX dbp: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?uri rdf:type yago:WikicatStatesOfTheUnitedStates ; dbp:densityrank ?rank } ORDER BY ASC(?rank) LIMIT 1
